# Supported Agents



Open Plugin is designed to work across AI coding agents. Support varies by component type — some agents support skills and MCP servers today, while other component types are newer.

export const Yes = () => <span style={{ display: 'inline-block', padding: '2px 10px', borderRadius: '9999px', fontSize: '13px', fontWeight: 500, backgroundColor: 'rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15)', color: 'rgb(34, 197, 94)' }}>Yes</span>

export const No = () => <span style={{ display: 'inline-block', padding: '2px 10px', borderRadius: '9999px', fontSize: '13px', fontWeight: 500, backgroundColor: 'rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15)', color: 'rgb(239, 68, 68)' }}>No</span>

Compatibility matrix [#compatibility-matrix]

| Component                                   |  Cursor | Claude Code |  Codex  | OpenCode |
| ------------------------------------------- | :-----: | :---------: | :-----: | :------: |
| [Skills](/docs/components/skills)           | <Yes /> |   <Yes />   |  <No /> |  <Yes /> |
| [Agents](/docs/components/agents)           |  <No /> |   <Yes />   |  <No /> |  <Yes /> |
| [Rules](/docs/components/rules)             | <Yes /> |   <Yes />   | <Yes /> |  <Yes /> |
| [Hooks](/docs/components/hooks)             | <Yes /> |   <Yes />   |  <No /> |  <Yes /> |
| [MCP Servers](/docs/components/mcp-servers) | <Yes /> |   <Yes />   |  <No /> |  <Yes /> |
| [LSP Servers](/docs/components/lsp-servers) | <Yes /> |    <No />   |  <No /> |  <No />  |

